### Version 0.0.2 - 2024-05-14
- Added the first functionalities!
- Added functions to rotate, resize, and change resolution of images
- Added functions to take difference/superposition of images 
- Added functions to change colours, saturation, contrast of images
- This is starting to take shape

### Version 0.0.1 - 2024-04-30
- Started the project!
- Added an image loader/saver

Intended final product/ideas:
- Definitely want graphical user interface
- Main: microscopy images
- Summarise: mean, std, etc-
- Basics: rotate, resize, saturations, etc.
- Set a scale, measure (with units), 
- convolutions, gaussian filters, mexican hats, etc.
- selection tool, colour picker etc.
- history of images and proper undo
- automatic counting and manual adjusting (once we have graphical interface), automatic edge and contour detection.



